title: Electric Kettle | KitchenAid
description: The KitchenAid® Electric kettle quickly and quietly brings water to a boil in minutes right at your countertop, desk or office. With a 5 cup capacity and removable base, it’s stylish and convenient. Learn more at http://www.kitchenaid.com/kitchenware/kettles/.
